general_feeling: At first it was really uncomfortable but then I kinda got used to it . It was also uncomfortable due to my high temperature; my glasses periodically fogged up.
challenges: It was a bit painful at first because the glasses were quite heavy for me. But then I got used to it. It was also a bit weird to get those strange looks because people thought I was filming them
act_impact: When I was on my way somewhere, it wasn't really comfortable because they're not really my size.
beh_adapt: I was trying to stay calm and ignore unpleasant things.
social: I guess in all public places.
improvements: I guess you could have a smaller size, and it could also be bit a bit lighter.
